{"tid":2229578,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"以921大地震模擬中國攻台 國民黨立委吳斯懷：民眾準備好了嗎？","createTime":"2020-10-04T13:23:30.000Z","updateTime":"2020-10-04T13:44:38.000Z","uid":337052,"like":0,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"b6720babcd226529945262c6b03764565380ad1d","tid":2229578,"uid":337052,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-04T13:23:30.000Z","msg":"<strong><span class=\"x-large\">以921大地震模擬中國攻台 吳斯懷：民眾準備好了嗎？</span></strong><br />\n   <br />\n<img src=\"https://img.ltn.com.tw/Upload/news/600/2020/10/04/phpSh3gYK.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.ltn.com.tw%2FUpload%2Fnews%2F600%2F2020%2F10%2F04%2FphpSh3gYK.jpg&h=2d5f8501&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n吳斯懷認為，台灣多年沒有經歷戰火威脅，民眾很難感受戰場景況，為讓民眾了解，吳斯懷以1999年發生的921大地震災區慘狀，模擬戰場狀況。（資料照）<br />\n<br />\n2020/10/04 20:39<br />\n〔即時新聞／綜合報導〕美國、中國持續在南海、台海附近進行軍事角力，<span class=\"red\">國民黨立委吳斯懷今（4日）指出，台灣多年沒有經歷戰火威脅，民眾很難感受戰場景況，為讓民眾了解，吳斯懷以1999年發生的921大地震災區慘狀，模擬戰場狀況，並問：「人民準備好了嗎？」。</span><br />\n<br />\n吳斯懷表示，地震發生3到4天內，災區如同遭受敵人首波攻擊，完全無法應變，吳列舉：<br />\n一、交通癱瘓：中部災區鐵、公路系統中斷，橋樑崩蹋（塌），許多災區形同孤島。<br />\n二、通訊中斷：市話、手機、網路全面中斷，災情無法傳遞。<br />\n三、水電停供：影響災民生存及夜間救災，持續時間過長，被難屍體及腐爛食物將可能引發疫病。<br />\n四、物資缺乏：前三項情況影響，飲水、食物、醫療資源缺乏，災情不明、交通中斷，救援物資無法及時送達災民手中。<br />\n五、搶救困難：軍隊第一天迅速投入，因為上述情況，災情不明，兵力派遣、機具調度非常困難，延宕搶救生命時機。<br />\n<br />\n吳斯懷認為，地震3、4天後在國軍全力投入兵力，災區才逐漸恢復指揮掌握。首先，派遣直升機空中偵察災情，運用特戰部隊徒步進入山區鄉村掌握災情；架設軍用通訊系統，開設中繼台，恢復通訊；搶通部分重要道路橋樑，以利搶救生命及人員物資輸送；統一調配物資，及時滿足災民需求；迅速處理遺體，避免產生疫病。<br />\n<br />\n吳斯懷強調，這只是中部災區的場景，中央政府、國軍及南北其他縣市沒有災情、或災情較輕微，可以全力支援，仍需要幾天時間才能恢復掌握，應變搶救。如果台海戰爭全面開打，損害必然遍及全國，國軍投入應戰，各地方政府自顧不暇，民眾只能自求多福。戰場景況如此，吳問：「政府準備好了嗎？人民準備好了嗎？」<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://news.ltn.com.tw/news/politics/breakingnews/3311494\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.ltn.com.tw%2Fnews%2Fpolitics%2Fbreakingnews%2F3311494&d=eUEb8trTAlhqW9E3j8wilwVsaiM9baN%2FEtUhsAXiQ7E%3D&h=7413de3c\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.ltn.com.tw%2Fnews%2Fpolitics%2Fbreakingnews%2F3311494&h=08050664\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://news.ltn.com.tw/news/politics/breakingnews/3311494</a>"},{"pid":"24a67f98ead0b9af4158eee8a49dcca8eeaffdd7","tid":2229578,"uid":21545,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-04T13:24:58.000Z","msg":"又係呢條pk <img src=\"/assets/faces/big/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"46b79fbefb18a6d4aa0662b844927a8ec17ac7b8","tid":2229578,"uid":337052,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-04T13:25:11.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/sz.huai.wu.2020/posts/187104529600346\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2Fsz.huai.wu.2020%2Fposts%2F187104529600346&d=eUEb8trTAlhqW9E3j8wilwVsaiM9baN%2FEtUhsAXiQ7E%3D&h=77e7ce3f\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/sz.huai.wu.2020/posts/187104529600346</a>"},{"pid":"2077710b3d88e2e415d58f58e72ecd4dc0f11247","tid":2229578,"uid":337052,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-10-04T13:25:39.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://scontent.ftpe7-3.fna.fbcdn.net/v/t1.0-0/s600x600/120491518_187104419600357_6909050814594743345_o.jpg?_nc_cat=102&amp;_nc_sid=8bfeb9&amp;_nc_ohc=3Z2tyN8N8BYAX_0rhoV&amp;_nc_ht=scontent.ftpe7-3.fna&amp;tp=7&amp;oh=5c2125bb7c37d910125255304ce0c0f3&amp;oe=5F9EF7D6\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fscontent.ftpe7-3.fna.fbcdn.net%2Fv%2Ft1.0-0%2Fs600x600%2F120491518_187104419600357_6909050814594743345_o.jpg%3F_nc_cat%3D102%26_nc_sid%3D8bfeb9%26_nc_ohc%3D3Z2tyN8N8BYAX_0rhoV%26_nc_ht%3Dscontent.ftpe7-3.fna%26tp%3D7%26oh%3D5c2125bb7c37d910125255304ce0c0f3%26oe%3D5F9EF7D6&h=ffaf474b&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"4e28c214f81883f4b961a9196af62665dbe44720","tid":2229578,"uid":251732,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"2077710b3d88e2e415d58f58e72ecd4dc0f11247","tid":2229578,"uid":337052,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-10-04T13:25:39.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://scontent.ftpe7-3.fna.fbcdn